Noyer Says Any Reduction in Greek Debtload Must Be ‘Voluntary’

-- B y   M a r k   D e e n
-- 
2011-10-16T16:39:33Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/noyer-says-any-reduction-in-greek-debtload-must-be-voluntary-.html
European Central Bank  governing
council member  Christian Noyer  said holders of Greek government
bonds may have to take bigger writedowns on those bonds than
agreed in July, though any such reduction must be “voluntary.”
He spoke on TV5 Monde.  To contact the reporter on this story:
